1)WRITE A QUERY THAT LISTS EACH ORDER NUMBER FOLLOWED BY THE NAME OF THE CUSTOMER WHO MADE THE ORDER

kd4_rahul_83497@localhost>select ORDERS.Onum,CUSTOMERS.Cname from ORDERS join CUSTOMERS on ORDERS.Cnum=CUSTOMERS.Cnum;
